{"tid":1082931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解隔離一個分化post都可以咁多正評","createTime":"2019-03-29T09:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T23:33:00.000Z","uid":33381,"like":52,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"43d9bca7dd09c299604984f2bcb7b2bbf850752d","tid":1082931,"uid":33381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪我同嗰邊樓主生活喺平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我眼見連登好多post都踩緊香港人<br />\n但點解都可以咁撚多正評<br />\n<br />\n去旅行會踩香港人影衰曬<br />\n貪小便宜 又嘈又冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港男又話港女全部都係雞<br />\n日韓台都算 連登仔話寧願娶大陸女人都唔要港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港女又踩港男又矮又毒又小家<br />\n唔識打扮冇個人風格<br />\n<br />\n返工又話地鐵加價乜乜柒柒都照仆住搭<br />\n打風打到乜撚都爛曬都要返工好似隻狗咁奴性重到<br />\n政治又會話人港豬 返工不了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有屌蝗屌蝻有咩問題 <br />\n根本我地就唔係純粹因爲覺得自己優越啲先屌佢地<br />\n我知香港人係有好多缺點<br />\n上面講嘅都一定有啲係發生緊<br />\n但點解要妄自菲薄到咁樣<br />\n<br />\n同埋  對自己國人身份覺得自豪有咩問題<br />\n我生於<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港國</span></span>我自豪<br />\n雖然....<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我真係好鍾意香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0077b26252be55ff4f1bba45e7cd778e9141b2","tid":1082931,"uid":95637,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"講事實點解唔得"},{"pid":"1014025d78ae4b0f4bfe61d2c2894e828508bf04","tid":1082931,"uid":33381,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"cf0077b26252be55ff4f1bba45e7cd778e9141b2","tid":1082931,"uid":95637,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"講事實點解唔得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"有啲香港人係會貪小便宜 有咩大是大非就返工不了<br />\n呢啲係事實<br />\n佢講到我地覺得自己高高在上就踩低其他國家嘅人<br />\n但蝻蝗平日嘅形象我地有眼見啦<br />\n形容到香港人因為要踩低人地嚟抬高自己我覺得係錯logic囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋每個國家嘅人都有缺點<br />\n純粹唔明點解一開呢啲分化post就一定好多人正評<br />\n其實香港人都唔係咁差姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642733daa14a26890f469e2c2100771ea65d7e80","tid":1082931,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔係中國人咩<br />\n崇洋媚外係dna黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91089dc1609ad6ce9d0047ed570531deefcfebd3","tid":1082931,"uid":67237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1014025d78ae4b0f4bfe61d2c2894e828508bf04","tid":1082931,"uid":33381,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"cf0077b26252be55ff4f1bba45e7cd778e9141b2","tid":1082931,"uid":95637,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"講事實點解唔得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"有啲香港人係會貪小便宜 有咩大是大非就返工不了<br />\n呢啲係事實<br />\n佢講到我地覺得自己高高在上就踩低其他國家嘅人<br />\n但蝻蝗平日嘅形象我地有眼見啦<br />\n形容到香港人因為要踩低人地嚟抬高自己我覺得係錯logic囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋每個國家嘅人都有缺點<br />\n純粹唔明點解一開呢啲分化post就一定好多人正評<br />\n其實香港人都唔係咁差姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"香港人同支那人最相似個位其實唔係貪<br />\n而係鍾意自相殘殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec087c1f22dedc55f5f38b6ab7ee7f3e948abef4","tid":1082931,"uid":130695,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1014025d78ae4b0f4bfe61d2c2894e828508bf04","tid":1082931,"uid":33381,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"cf0077b26252be55ff4f1bba45e7cd778e9141b2","tid":1082931,"uid":95637,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"講事實點解唔得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:24:57.000Z","msg":"有啲香港人係會